import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { useHistory, useLocation } from "react-router-dom"; import { toAbsoluteUrl } from "../../../../../../../../../_metronic/_helpers"; import SVG from "react-inlinesvg"; import { Card } from "react-bootstrap"; import { CardBody } from "../../../../../../../../../_metronic/_partials/controls"; export default function ProposalReceived() { let history = useHistory(); let routeLocation = useLocation(); const [productsList, setProductsList] = useState([]); const [proposalInfo, setProposalInfo] = useState({}); const [returnReceiveCartList, setReturnReceiveCartList] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { document.getElementById('full-screen-close-icon').style.display = "none"; console.log("routeLocation.state.state=", routeLocation.state.state) setProposalInfo(routeLocation.state.state); // setProductsList(routeLocation.state.state) }, []) const handleBackToListPage = () => { history.push('/inventory/stock/sales-return/sales-return-list'); } const openFullscreen = () => { const elem = document.getElementById("myFullScreen"); elem.classList.add("scroll-product-search"); elem.requestFullscreen(); document.getElementById('full-screen-icon').style.display = "none" document.getElementById('full-screen-close-icon').style.display = "inline-block" } const closeFullscreen = () => { const elem = document.getElementById("myFullScreen"); elem.classList.remove("scroll-product-search"); document.exitFullscreen(); document.getElementById('full-screen-icon').style.display = "inline-block" document.getElementById('full-screen-close-icon').style.display = "none" } const handleReceivedChange = (product) => { document.getElementById('receive-id-' + product.id).classList.add('d-none') document.getElementById('received-id-' + product.id).classList.remove('d-none') const temp = [...returnReceiveCartList] temp.push(product) setReturnReceiveCartList(temp) } const handleRemovetoCart = (data) => { document.getElementById('receive-id-' + data.id).classList.remove('d-none') document.getElementById('received-id-' + data.id).classList.add('d-none') const temp = [...returnReceiveCartList] const index = temp.findIndex(obj => obj.id == data.id); temp.splice(index, 1); setReturnReceiveCartList(temp) } console.log(returnReceiveCartList) return ( <>
